{"title_page": "No Shame (5 Seconds of Summer song)", "text_new": "{{Infobox song\n| name       = No Shame\n| cover      = NoShame5SoS.jpg\n| alt        =\n| type       = single\n| artist     = [[5 Seconds of Summer]]\n| album      = [[Calm (album)|Calm]]\n| released   = 5 February 2020\n| format     = \n*[[Music download|Digital download]]\n*[[Streaming media|streaming]]\n| recorded   = \n| studio     =\n| venue      =\n| genre      = [[New wave]], [[industrial rock]]\n| length     = 3:10\n| label      = \n*[[Interscope Records|Interscope]]\n*[[Polydor Records|Polydor]]\n| writer     = \n*[[5 Seconds of Summer|Calum Hood]]\n*[[5 Seconds of Summer|Luke Hemmings]]\n*[[5 Seconds of Summer|Ashton Irwin]]\n*[[5 Seconds of Summer|Michael Clifford]]\n*[[Ali Tamposi|Alexandra Tamposi]]\n*[[Andrew Watt (musician)|Andrew Wotman]]\n*Nathan Perez\n*[[Donna Lewis]]\n| producer   = \n*[[Andrew Watt (musician)|Andrew Watt]]\n*Happy Perez\n| prev_title = [[Teeth (5 Seconds of Summer song)|Teeth]]\n| prev_year  = 2019\n| next_title = [[Old Me (5 Seconds of Summer song)|Old Me]]\n| next_year  = 2020\n| misc       = \n}}\n\"'''No Shame'''\" is a song by Australian [[pop rock]] band [[5 Seconds of Summer]], released on 5 February 2020 as the third single from the band's fourth studio album ''[[Calm (album)|Calm]]''.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/8550208/5-seconds-of-summer-no-shame-calm-album|title=5 Seconds of Summer Reveal New Song \"No Shame\", Announce ''Calm'' Album: See When It's Coming|last=Weatherby|first=Taylor|website=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|date=5 February 2020|accessdate=1 April 2020}}</ref> The song was written by [[5 Seconds of Summer|Calum Hood]], [[5 Seconds of Summer|Luke Hemmings]], [[5 Seconds of Summer|Ashton Irwin]], [[5 Seconds of Summer|Michael Clifford]], [[Ali Tamposi|Alexandra Tamposi]], [[Andrew Watt (musician)|Andrew Wotman]], Nathan Perez and [[Donna Lewis]].\n\n==Music video==\nA music video to accompany the release of \"No Shame\" was first released onto YouTube on 7 February 2020 and has over 10 million views as of April 2020.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=69glFaMhGgc|title=5 Seconds of Summer - No Shame (Official Video)|publisher=[[YouTube]]|accessdate=1 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Charts==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2020)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br/>position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Australia ([[ARIA Charts|ARIA]])\n| 63\n|-\n{{single chart|Flanders Tip|33|artist=5 Seconds of Summer|song=No Shame|rowheader=true|accessdate=1 April 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Ireland3|56|artist=5 Seconds of Summer|rowheader=true|accessdate=1 April 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| New Zealand Hot Singles ([[Recorded Music NZ|RMNZ]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/hotsingles?chart=4820|title=NZ Hot Singles Chart|publisher=Recorded Music NZ|date=17 February 2020|accessdate=1 April 2020}}</ref>\n| 6\n|-\n{{single chart|UK|68|date=20200214|rowheader=true|accessdate=1 April 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Billboardbubbling100|12|artist=5 Seconds of Summer|rowheader=true|accessdate=1 April 2020}}\n|}\n\n==Release history==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n! scope=\"col\"| Region\n! scope=\"col\"| Date\n! scope=\"col\"| Format\n! scope=\"col\"| Label\n! scope=\"col\"| {{Abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Various\n| 5 February 2020\n| \n[[Music download|Digital download]]\n[[Streaming media|streaming]]\n| \n[[Interscope Records|Interscope]]\n[[Polydor Records|Polydor]]\n| \n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{5 Seconds of Summer}}\n\n[[Category:2020 singles]]\n[[Category:2020 songs]]\n[[Category:5 Seconds of Summer songs]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Ali Tamposi]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Andrew Watt (musician)]]\n\n{{2020s-single-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox song\n| name       = No Shame\n| cover      = NoShame5SoS.jpg\n| alt        =\n| type       = single\n| artist     = [[5 Seconds of Summer]]\n| album      = [[Calm (album)|Calm]]\n| released   = 5 February 2020\n| format     = \n*[[Music download|Digital download]]\n*[[Streaming media|streaming]]\n| recorded   = \n| studio     =\n| venue      =\n| genre      = \n| length     = 3:10\n| label      = \n*[[Interscope Records|Interscope]]\n*[[Polydor Records|Polydor]]\n| writer     = \n*[[5 Seconds of Summer|Calum Hood]]\n*[[5 Seconds of Summer|Luke Hemmings]]\n*[[5 Seconds of Summer|Ashton Irwin]]\n*[[5 Seconds of Summer|Michael Clifford]]\n*[[Ali Tamposi|Alexandra Tamposi]]\n*[[Andrew Watt (musician)|Andrew Wotman]]\n*Nathan Perez\n*[[Donna Lewis]]\n| producer   = \n*[[Andrew Watt (musician)|Andrew Watt]]\n*Happy Perez\n| prev_title = [[Teeth (5 Seconds of Summer song)|Teeth]]\n| prev_year  = 2019\n| next_title = [[Old Me (5 Seconds of Summer song)|Old Me]]\n| next_year  = 2020\n| misc       = \n}}\n\"'''No Shame'''\" is a song by Australian [[pop rock]] band [[5 Seconds of Summer]], released on 5 February 2020 as the third single from the band's fourth studio album ''[[Calm (album)|Calm]]''.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/8550208/5-seconds-of-summer-no-shame-calm-album|title=5 Seconds of Summer Reveal New Song \"No Shame\", Announce ''Calm'' Album: See When It's Coming|last=Weatherby|first=Taylor|website=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|date=5 February 2020|accessdate=1 April 2020}}</ref> The song was written by [[5 Seconds of Summer|Calum Hood]], [[5 Seconds of Summer|Luke Hemmings]], [[5 Seconds of Summer|Ashton Irwin]], [[5 Seconds of Summer|Michael Clifford]], [[Ali Tamposi|Alexandra Tamposi]], [[Andrew Watt (musician)|Andrew Wotman]], Nathan Perez and [[Donna Lewis]].\n\n==Music video==\nA music video to accompany the release of \"No Shame\" was first released onto YouTube on 7 February 2020 and has over 10 million views as of April 2020.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=69glFaMhGgc|title=5 Seconds of Summer - No Sha